Ingrid Chauvin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ingrid_Chauvin 0 Ingrid Chauvin (born 3 October 1973) is a French television and stage actress, known for her roles in the miniseries Méditerranée, Dolmen, and the police procedural series Femmes de loi.
